heading: Participate in Maxroll VoH Launch Race!
content: After an unfortunate delayed launch, Season 6 and Vessel of Hatred are finally here! At the occasion of Diablo 4 new expansion, Maxroll invites you to participate in our newest event, a Prove your strength to the Diablo 4 community by submitting proof of your Dark Citadel clear on Torment 4 difficulty and reap your rewards! We hope you enjoy the Season of Hatred Rising and the Vessel of Hatred expansion with the aid of our Season 6 compendium update. Our focus for the start of Season 6 is to make sure our are solid with all the new Item updates, new features and mechanic changes.
